def string_expansion(s):
    result = ""
    i = 0
    while i < len(s):
        num = ""
        while i < len(s) and s[i].isdigit():
            num += s[i]
            i += 1
        if num:
            num = int(num)
            i -= 1
            char = s[i]
            result += char * num
            i += 1
        else:
            result += s[i]
        i += 1
    return result
